hadiths[49]{hadithnumber,text}:
5381,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5382,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5383,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5384,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5385,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5386,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5387,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5388,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5389,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. aur ghaabhaa khajoor key maghz ko kehtey hain.
5390,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. aur ghaabhaa khajoor key maghz ko kehtey hain.
5391,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (goodey) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye ghalat hai. Abu Maimoon ko main nahin pahchaantaa.
5392,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal aur gaabhey (goodey) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye ghalat hai. Abu Maimoon ko main nahin pahchaantaa.
5393,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5394,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5395,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5396,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5397,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley, lootney waley aur jhapat kar chhin leney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Sufiyan (Sauri) ney Abu-Zubair sey nahin suna."
5398,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley, lootney waley aur jhapat kar chhin leney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Sufiyan (Sauri) ney Abu-Zubair sey nahin suna."
5399,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley, loot dalney waley aur jhapatney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. ibne Juraij ney bhi Abu-Zubair sey nahin suna."
5400,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley, loot dalney waley aur jhapatney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. ibne Juraij ney bhi Abu-Zubair sey nahin suna."
5401,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hui hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jhapat maar kar chhin ley janey waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5402,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hui hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jhapat maar kar chhin ley janey waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.
5403,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) ney farmaya : Esa bin Yunus, Fazal bin Musa, ibne Wahab, Muhammad bin Rabeea, Mukhlid bin Yazid aur Salma bin Saeed jo ke Basri aur qabile-bharosa hain (aur jinkey barey mein Muhammad bin Usman) ibne Abu-Safwaan ney kaha hai ke wo (Salma bin Saeed) apney zamaney key behtareen shakhs they, un sab ney ibne Juraij sey ye (mazkura) riwayat bayan ki hai lekin un (chhe Jaleelul-qadr aur qabile-bharosa ehale-ilm) main sey kisi eik ney bhi (Abu-Zubair se hadees riwayat hui hai)  nahin kaha. aur mera nahin khayal ke us (ibne Juraij) ney Abu-Zubair sey suna ho. (Wallahu-Aalam)."
5404,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) ney farmaya : Esa bin Yunus, Fazal bin Musa, ibne Wahab, Muhammad bin Rabeea, Mukhlid bin Yazid aur Salma bin Saeed jo ke Basri aur qabile-bharosa hain (aur jinkey barey mein Muhammad bin Usman) ibne Abu-Safwaan ney kaha hai ke wo (Salma bin Saeed) apney zamaney key behtareen shakhs they, un sab ney ibne Juraij sey ye (mazkura) riwayat bayan ki hai lekin un (chhe Jaleelul-qadr aur qabile-bharosa ehale-ilm) main sey kisi eik ney bhi (Abu-Zubair se hadees riwayat hui hai)  nahin kaha. aur mera nahin khayal ke us (ibne Juraij) ney Abu-Zubair sey suna ho. (Wallahu-Aalam)."
5405,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jhapat maar kar chhupney waley, loot dalney waley (daaku) aur khayanat karney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5406,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jhapat maar kar chhupney waley, loot dalney waley (daaku) aur khayanat karney waley ka haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5407,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke khayanat karney waley ko haath kaatney ki saza nahin di ja sakti. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : Ash-as bin Sawar zaeef hai.
5408,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke khayanat karney waley ko haath kaatney ki saza nahin di ja sakti. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : Ash-as bin Sawar zaeef hai.
5409,"Hazrat Haris bin Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is ney to chori ki hai? aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney phir kaha : Allah key Rasool ! is ney to sirf chori ki hai? aap ney farmaya : is ka haath kaat do. us ney phir chori kar li. phir us ka paon kaat diya gaya. phir us ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key daur mein chori kar li yahan tak ke eik eik kar key uskey chaaron haath paon kaat diye gaey. phir us ney paanchwin dafa chori kar li. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is (ki haisiyat ka khub ilm tha). tabhi to aap ney pehli dafa hi farmaya tha : isey qatl kar do. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey chand quraishi nojawanon key supurd kar diya ke isey qatl kar den. un nojawanon mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they. wo hukumat key badey sahuqeen they. wo kehney lagey : tum mujhey apna (waqti) Ameer bana lo. unhoney in ko Ameer bana liya. jab wo usey maartay they, tab dusrey maartay they yahan tak ke is tarah unhoney us chor ko qatl kar diya."
5410,"Hazrat Haris bin Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is ney to chori ki hai? aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney phir kaha : Allah key Rasool ! is ney to sirf chori ki hai? aap ney farmaya : is ka haath kaat do. us ney phir chori kar li. phir us ka paon kaat diya gaya. phir us ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key daur mein chori kar li yahan tak ke eik eik kar key uskey chaaron haath paon kaat diye gaey. phir us ney paanchwin dafa chori kar li. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is (ki haisiyat ka khub ilm tha). tabhi to aap ney pehli dafa hi farmaya tha : isey qatl kar do. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey chand quraishi nojawanon key supurd kar diya ke isey qatl kar den. un nojawanon mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they. wo hukumat key badey sahuqeen they. wo kehney lagey : tum mujhey apna (waqti) Ameer bana lo. unhoney in ko Ameer bana liya. jab wo usey maartay they, tab dusrey maartay they yahan tak ke is tarah unhoney us chor ko qatl kar diya."
5411,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya. (is ka daayan haath) kaat do. us ka haath kaat diya gaya. phir usey dobara (chori karney par) laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka baayan paon kaat do. us ka paon kaat diya gaya. teesri martaba phir usey laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney to sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka (baayan haath) kaat do. phir usey chauthi martaba (pakad kar) laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : is ko qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka (daayan paon) kaat do. paanchwin baar phir usey laya gaya to aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum usey utha kar oonton key eik baadey mein ley gaey to wo chit let gaya. phir achcha apney (katey huye) haathon aur paon par bhag utha. oont (dar kar) bidakney lagey. logon ney bhag kar dobara us ko pakad liya. us ney phir isi tarah kiya. phir teesri dafa us ko pakda to hamney us ko patthar maar maar kar qatl kar diya. phir hamney usey eik khadan ya ghaddhey mein dal diya aur ooper sey patthar phenk diye. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke ye hadees munkir hai. aur Musab bin Sabit hadees mein qawi (aur mazboot) nahin."
5412,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya. (is ka daayan haath) kaat do. us ka haath kaat diya gaya. phir usey dobara (chori karney par) laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka baayan paon kaat do. us ka paon kaat diya gaya. teesri martaba phir usey laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney to sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka (baayan haath) kaat do. phir usey chauthi martaba (pakad kar) laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : is ko qatl kar do. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney sirf chori ki hai. aap ney farmaya : is ka (daayan paon) kaat do. paanchwin baar phir usey laya gaya to aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum usey utha kar oonton key eik baadey mein ley gaey to wo chit let gaya. phir achcha apney (katey huye) haathon aur paon par bhag utha. oont (dar kar) bidakney lagey. logon ney bhag kar dobara us ko pakad liya. us ney phir isi tarah kiya. phir teesri dafa us ko pakda to hamney us ko patthar maar maar kar qatl kar diya. phir hamney usey eik khadan ya ghaddhey mein dal diya aur ooper sey patthar phenk diye. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke ye hadees munkir hai. aur Musab bin Sabit hadees mein qawi (aur mazboot) nahin."
5413,Hazrat Basar bin Abi Irtaat (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : safar mein chor key haath na kaatey jaeyn.
5414,Hazrat Basar bin Abi Irtaat (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : safar mein chor key haath na kaatey jaeyn.
5415,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi ghulam chori kar ley to usey bech do agar-che nisf (aadhi) qeemat par bikey. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (hadees ka raawi) umr bin Abu-Salma hadees mein qawi nahin.
5416,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi ghulam chori kar ley to usey bech do agar-che nisf (aadhi) qeemat par bikey. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (hadees ka raawi) umr bin Abu-Salma hadees mein qawi nahin.
5417,"Hazrat Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Banu Qureza key qaidiyon mein shamil tha. (faisley key mutabiq) dekha jata tha ke jis qaidi key zere-naf baal ugey hotey they, usey qatl kar diya jata tha aur jis key zere-naf baal nahin ugey hotey they, usey zinda chhod diya jata tha aur qatl nahin kiya jata tha."
5418,"Hazrat Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Banu Qureza key qaidiyon mein shamil tha. (faisley key mutabiq) dekha jata tha ke jis qaidi key zere-naf baal ugey hotey they, usey qatl kar diya jata tha aur jis key zere-naf baal nahin ugey hotey they, usey zinda chhod diya jata tha aur qatl nahin kiya jata tha."
5419,"Hazrat Ibne-Muheriz sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey chor ka haath uski gardan mein latkaaney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya (ye ) sunnat hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chor ka haath kaat kar uski gardan mein latka diya tha."
5420,"Hazrat Ibne-Muheriz sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey chor ka haath uski gardan mein latkaaney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya (ye ) sunnat hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chor ka haath kaat kar uski gardan mein latka diya tha."
5421,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Muhaireez bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : farmaain kya chor ka haath uskey galey mein latkana sunnat hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaat kar uskey galey mein latka diya. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : (is hadees aur sabiqa (pichhli) hadees ka raawi) Hujjaaj bin Irtaat zaeef hai. uski hadees qabile-hujjat nahin hoti.
5422,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Muhaireez bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : farmaain kya chor ka haath uskey galey mein latkana sunnat hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaat kar uskey galey mein latka diya. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : (is hadees aur sabiqa (pichhli) hadees ka raawi) Hujjaaj bin Irtaat zaeef hai. uski hadees qabile-hujjat nahin hoti.
5423,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab chor par had nafiz (laagu) kar di jaey to is par chori ka tawaan (jurmana) na dala jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha : ye (hadees) mursal hai aur sabit nahin hai.
5424,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab chor par had nafiz (laagu) kar di jaey to is par chori ka tawaan (jurmana) na dala jaeyga. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney kaha : ye (hadees) mursal hai aur sabit nahin hai.
5425,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah uskey Rasool par eman lana.
5426,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah uskey Rasool par eman lana.
5427,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi Khas'ami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : aisa eman jis mein zarra bhar shak na ho, wo jihad jis mein kisi qism ki khayanat na ho aur nek aur pak hajj."
5428,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi Khas'ami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : aisa eman jis mein zarra bhar shak na ho, wo jihad jis mein kisi qism ki khayanat na ho aur nek aur pak hajj."
5429,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen cheezen aisi hain ke jis shakhs mein bhi pai jaeyn, eman us ko lazeez malum hota hai. (usey eman mein maza aaney lagta hai.) Allah aur us ka Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon. uski mohabbat aur narazi khalis Allah Taala key liye ho. azeem bhadakti aag mein gir padna usey Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek thehraney sey ziyada pasand ho."
